Subject: [ghostium] navigator.plugins / mimeTypes hook

Spec-E wiring. Anchors at top of ``dom_plugin_array.cc``. The real
call into ``FingerprintNoiseSource::PluginsOverride`` lands inside
``DOMPluginArray::UpdatePluginData``: when the override returns true
(including the explicit empty-list case), the upstream plugin
enumeration is replaced wholesale with the profile's spec list. The
explicit empty list is meaningful: it makes ``navigator.plugins``
empty without forcing every plugin-removal field to be set
individually.

The companion ``DOMMimeTypeArray`` is materialised from the same
plugin specs (one entry per ``mimeTypes`` string), so this single
hook covers both ``navigator.plugins`` and ``navigator.mimeTypes``.

